; good_ledger.beancount — exercises every validation checker and
; is expected to produce zero validation errors.

option "title" "Good Ledger"
option "operating_currency" "USD"

2024-01-01 open Assets:Cash               USD
2024-01-01 open Assets:Bank               USD
2024-01-01 open Income:Salary             USD
2024-01-01 open Expenses:Food             USD
2024-01-01 open Equity:Opening-Balances

; Pad establishes opening balance; resolved by the balance assertion below.
2024-01-02 pad Assets:Bank Equity:Opening-Balances

2024-01-10 * "Employer" "January salary"
  Assets:Bank         1000.00 USD
  Income:Salary      -1000.00 USD

; Balance assertion resolves the pad and verifies the running balance.
2024-02-01 balance Assets:Bank            1500.00 USD

2024-02-05 * "Grocery" "Weekly shop"
  Expenses:Food          50.00 USD
  Assets:Cash           -50.00 USD

; Explicit tolerance on a balance assertion.
2024-02-10 balance Assets:Cash             -50.00 USD ~ 0.01 USD

; Built-in custom "assert" handler: running balance check.
2024-02-11 custom "assert" Assets:Cash    -50.00 USD

2024-02-20 note Assets:Bank "Reconciled with statement"

2024-12-31 close Expenses:Food
